item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: bill
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Features
item.dc:creator: bill
item.content:encoded:
Maintenance Mode

Contact Form Portfolio /team  

2 menus more social menu

 
SOCIAL
Enable social media icons and easy share functionality with the click of a button. Use the available social media icons or upload your own.  

1 click color selector

Use one of 6 pre made colors or create your own (unlimited) color. It is easy.
LIFETIME UPDATES
Be is always up to date. We constantly listen to our customers and we add new features every week. We take good care of your business the same way you do.
OPTIMIZED FOR SPEED
The theme is fully optimized. Well written code and optimized images helped us create such a fast theme. Your visitors will love how fast your website is. Custom CSS You can do it without modify the theme. Just go to our Customize Panel. You will not lose them when you update the theme.

Child Theme

Child theme is included in the package.
BROWSERS COMPATIBLE
Every part of the theme has been thoroughly investigated and works perfectly with all available browsers, whether they are Internet Explorer, Safari, Chrome, Firefox or even Opera.  
SEO READY
This follow the best SEO practices to help rank your website higher. Compatibility with plugins like Yoast or All in One SEO is fully ensured.  
AUTO UPDATES
You can receive notifications and update theme automatically.

BUILT-IN TRANSLATOR & MULTILINGUAL READY

The built-in translator allows you to translate easily the website into another language. If you prefer a multilingual website, you can use the WPML plugin which is supported by Be.
WIDE/BOXED LAYOUT
Choose between boxed and wide and wide layout.
ADVANCED TYPOGRAPHY
Use Google or upload custom fonts, set sizes, style, weight and much more. Be gives you full control over the fonts.
PARALLAX EFFECT & VIDEO BACKGROUND
Create awesome pages with the smooth parallax effect that everyone loves. You can upload videos, put text, images, buttons or other graphical elements and enjoy the great looking sections.
RESPONSIVE READY
Be is fully responsive. Your customers will love how your website looks on tablets and mobile devices.
1 CLICK DEMO IMPORT
Choose between over 100 pre-made layouts and import any with just one click. Build websites within seconds as easily as never before.
POWERFUL ADMIN PANEL
Muffin options panel allows users to customize the theme in an easy and simple way. Theres no need to code anything thanks to all the amazing options that are included in the theme.
CSS3 ANIMATIONS
Choose from our collection of fluid CSS3 animations, carefully designed for a smooth and seamless experience.

WOOCOMMERCE COMPATIBLE
Set up a fully operational online shop in no time with Bridge and the free, easy-to-use WooCommerce plugin.

Premium Features

Gallery

For the gallery posts and the pages, you can use Nivo slider or Flex Slider.

Unlimited sidebars

Add different sidebar for each page and post, you can use our custom or default widgets on each sidebar.

Full option panel

With the full option panel, you can change fonts, add sidebars, manage slides and more

Page templates

Is possible use the masonry layout or set the portfolio page.

Masonry layout

With the masonry layout, you can create a layout similar to Pinterest, for display the articles, the category and the portfolio section.

Portfolio section

You can add and display your works and give a modern layout, thanks to the masonry layout.

Custom widgets

Besides to the default WordPress widgets, the theme have other seven different custom widgets.

Shortcodes

With the shortcodes, you can add a dinamic contents into your posts and pages.

Shortcodes generator

For only WordPress 3.9.0 and higher versions is available a dynamic shortcode generator.

Google fonts

You can choose and use over 600 different fonts, for the logo, the menu and the titles.

Documentation

A complete pdf manual is included with the theme, in English and Italian language.

Free support

For any question and problem, you can request a quickly support, is necessary open a new ticket.

Font Awesome icons

You can choose over 369 different icons, from the Font Awesome collection.

Video tutorials

See how is easy compose your site, with our videotutorials.

Sample data

Load our sample data from WordPress importer, with all pages, articles, menu and portfolio items.

Unlimited colors

Choose a color for the links, the backgrounds, the slogan and so on.
